p.k: Robin tries to destroy some pesky mocking birds but they come back bigger, stronger, and ready to mock. / Cyborg has a star-crossed crush on Jinx, the cutest member of The Hive. / Cyborg and Beast Boy annoy the other Titans by refusing to say anything but "Waffles." / Starfire convinces the reluctant Titans to try defeating their enemies with compassion rather than violence. / Robin refuses to give the Titans any more orders so that they'll learn to think for themselves. Instead the Titans start taking their cues from fortune cookies.
